msgctxt "392_Akiyama"
msgid "Ever heard of 777 Town?"
msgstr "¿Conoces 777 Town?"

msgctxt "404_Noa"
msgid "Oh, I have! It's the game that lets you play pachinko and slots on your PC or cell, right?"
msgstr "¡Oh, creo que sí! Es ese juego que te permite jugar pachinko y pachislots desde tu PC o celular, ¿verdad?"

msgctxt "416_Akiyama"
msgid "That's the one. Do you play?"
msgstr "Ese mismo. ¿Acaso Noa-chan lo estuvo jugando?"

msgctxt "428_Noa"
msgid "Yep! I love pachinko. I go to pachinko parlors a lot."
msgstr "Je, je, je, je. ♪\n"\n"La verdad es que me encanta el pachinko. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default> Usualmente voy bastante a los salones de pachinko. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "440_Akiyama"
msgid "Wow, really?"
msgstr "¡No te creo! ¿De verdad?"

msgctxt "452_Noa"
msgid "Yeah, I even play 777 Town at home."
msgstr "Aunque es un secreto, mis padres no saben. ♪\n"\n"A veces también juego 777 Town en casa. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "464_Akiyama"
msgid "Ever heard of Amoebatar?"
msgstr "¿Sabes algo sobre Amoebatar?"

msgctxt "476_Noa"
msgid "Yeah! My friends and I are all on it."
msgstr "¡Por supuesto! ♪\n"\n"Todos mis amigos tienen uno. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>\n"\n"¡Y obvio que yo también! <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "488_Akiyama"
msgid "You don't say? I guess it's really booming."
msgstr "Por lo visto todo el mundo tiene uno, incluso los famosos, uh."

msgctxt "500_Noa"
msgid "Why don't you try it out?"
msgstr "¿Por qué no lo prueba, Akiyama-san?"

msgctxt "512_Akiyama"
msgid "If it's as great as everyone says, I just might."
msgstr "Si es tan bueno como todos dicen, podría intentarlo..."

msgctxt "524_Akiyama"
msgid "Hear about the ghost in the underground mall?"
msgstr "¿Escuchaste sobre el fantasma que hay en el centro comercial subterráneo?"

msgctxt "536_Noa"
msgid "Huh? A ghost!?"
msgstr "¿¡Eh!? ¿¡Un fantasma!?"

msgctxt "548_Akiyama"
msgid "Yeah. When they were building the mall, a construction worker died in an accident."
msgstr "Sí. Dicen que durante las obras de construcción del centro comercial, uno de los trabajadores murió en un accidente."

msgctxt "560_Akiyama"
msgid "Now, night after night, his ghost appears to wander the empty mall."
msgstr "Ahora, cuando ya es de muy noche, su fantasma aparece deambulando por el vacío centro comercial..."

msgctxt "572_Noa"
msgid "No way! Is that really true?"
msgstr "¡¿Quééé?! ¿Eso es verdad?"

msgctxt "584_Akiyama"
msgid "As far as I know. Don't worry, I'll protect you from any ghosts."
msgstr "Tampoco tienes que preocuparte tanto. Si aparece un fantasma, te protegeré."

msgctxt "596_Noa"
msgid "Heh. That's reassuring. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Ahaha. ♪\n"\n"Qué alivio. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "608_Akiyama"
msgid "Hear about the footbaths at Yunosono Hot Springs? You don't take off your clothes, so men and women can go in together."
msgstr "¿Has oído hablar de los baños de pies de las Aguas termales Yunosono? No hay necesidad de quitarse la ropa, así que hombres y mujeres pueden ir juntos."

msgctxt "620_Noa"
msgid "Wow, I never knew. I could use a relaxing soak after ballet. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "¡Woah, no tenía ni idea! ♪\n"\n"De seguro es perfecto luego de una agotadora sesión de ballet. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "632_Akiyama"
msgid "Huh. You look pretty limber. I'm surprised you get stiff at all."
msgstr "Uh, pero tus músculos se ven bastante relajados ahora mismo. ¿De verdad se ponen todo tensos?"

msgctxt "644_Noa"
msgid "Well, not after ballet, but working as hostess takes its toll. Enough that a hot springs trip starts to sound really good."
msgstr "Bueno, dejando de lado el ballet, creo que el trabajo como hostess me deja toda tensionada... Una visita a las aguas termales suena bastante bien. ♪"

msgctxt "656_Akiyama"
msgid "Ah, I see."
msgstr "Bueno, tiene sentido..."

msgctxt "668_Akiyama"
msgid "Golf is getting pretty popular. A lot of couples go on golf dates nowadays."
msgstr "El golf se ha vuelto popular últimamente. Y al parecer las parejas van de citas a esos lugares."

msgctxt "680_Noa"
msgid "Yeah. Golf is great for venting frustration, too. Perfect for relieving stress."
msgstr "Eh, qué curioso. Bueno, el golf también es una excelente manera de aliviar el estrés. ♪"

msgctxt "692_Akiyama"
msgid "I know what you mean. You're a hard hitter, huh?"
msgstr "Jo, así que eres de las chicas que pegan con fuerza, ¿eh?"

msgctxt "704_Noa"
msgid "Hehe. It's the only satisfying way to play, don't you think?"
msgstr "Je, je, je. ♪\n"\n"Es la única forma satisfactoria de jugarlo, ¿no lo cree? <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "716_Akiyama"
msgid "Say, Noa, do you like liver? Liver contains some kind of acid that reverses aging in the brain."
msgstr "¿Te gusta el hígado, Noa-chan? Dicen que el hígado contiene ácido rarete que tiene efectos rejuvenecedores en el cerebro."

msgctxt "728_Noa"
msgid "Wow, really? I don't eat that much liver."
msgstr "Guau, ¿de verdad?\n"\n"Bueno, yo soy más de comer yakiniku. ♪"

msgctxt "740_Akiyama"
msgid "It's good for your memory too, so you'll stay sharp when you're old."
msgstr "Es bueno para tu memoria, y dice que te ayudará a prevenir el deterioro mental por vejez."

msgctxt "752_Noa"
msgid "Oh? Then it'd be great for you, since you can't even remember the name of the acid."
msgstr "¡Ey, pero eso suena perfecto para usted! ♪\n"\n"Al parecer ni recuerda el nombre del \"ácido rarete\", ji. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "764_Akiyama"
msgid "Hey now, that's got nothing to do with my memory. I only heard it in passing somewhere."
msgstr "Oi, oi, no es que tenga problemas de memoria, es que era solo un recuerdo vago..."

msgctxt "776_Akiyama"
msgid "They say pole dancing's great for losing weight."
msgstr "Dicen que el pole dance es bueno para bajar de peso."

msgctxt "788_Noa"
msgid "It must be! Any kind of dancing burns fat all over your body."
msgstr "Seguro que sí. ♪\n"\n"Cualquier tipo de baile te ayuda a quemar grasas por todo el cuerpo, de seguro terminas con una figura esbelta. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "800_Akiyama"
msgid "Oh, that's right. You do ballet, right? I guess you don't need to slim down."
msgstr "Ah, es verdad que practicas ballet. Supongo que no necesitas bajar de peso..."

msgctxt "812_Akiyama"
msgid "Sweet sake is all the rage now. Women like to have it at Sushi Gin these days."
msgstr "Parece que últimamente el sake dulce está de moda. En Sushi Gin la mujeres lo piden regularmente junto a sus comidas."

msgctxt "824_Noa"
msgid "Wow, they have that now? Sounds tasty!"
msgstr "¿Eh? ¿Ahora hay un trago como ese?\n"\n"¡Suena a que es riquísimo! ♪"

msgctxt "836_Akiyama"
msgid "And it isn't that high in alcohol. It's the perfect match for a fancy dinner."
msgstr "No tiene un alto contenido de alcohol, y su sabor afrutado lo hace perfecto para una cena elegante."

msgctxt "848_Noa"
msgid "Sounds great. Now all I need is someone to take me out to a fancy dinner."
msgstr "¡Je, je, je, qué bien suena! ♪\n"\n"¿Habrá alguien que me quiera invita a una cena elegante, umh?"

msgctxt "896_Akiyama"
msgid "So about 777 Town..."
msgstr "Acerca del 777 Town..."

msgctxt "908_Noa"
msgid "Oh, did you try it out? Isn't it fun?"
msgstr "Oh, did you try it out? Isn't it fun?"

msgctxt "920_Akiyama"
msgid "Actually, not yet. I was hoping you could tell me more about it."
msgstr "Actually, not yet. I was hoping you could tell me more about it."

msgctxt "932_Akiyama"
msgid "So about Amoebatar..."
msgstr "Acerca del Amoebatar..."

msgctxt "944_Noa"
msgid "Did you make an account? It's great fun, isn't it?"
msgstr "Did you make an account? It's great fun, isn't it?"

msgctxt "956_Akiyama"
msgid "Yeah. Let's chat together sometime."
msgstr "Yeah. Let's chat together sometime."

msgctxt "968_Noa"
msgid "Sure thing. That is, if you request me next time you're here. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Sure thing. That is, if you request me next time you're here. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "980_Akiyama"
msgid "Oh, come on!"
msgstr "¡Oh, vamos!"

msgctxt "992_Akiyama"
msgid "So about that ghost in the underground mall..."
msgstr "Acerca del fantasma del centro comercial..."

msgctxt "1004_Noa"
msgid "Oh! I saw it the other day!"
msgstr "Oh! I saw it the other day!"

msgctxt "1016_Akiyama"
msgid "Whoa, really?"
msgstr "Whoa, really?"

msgctxt "1028_Noa"
msgid "I saw some people fighting in a parking lot. Some yakuza had this one man surrounded."
msgstr "I saw some people fighting in a parking lot. Some yakuza had this one man surrounded."

msgctxt "1040_Noa"
msgid "All of a sudden, a blue flame－kinda like a spirit－enveloped the man!"
msgstr "All of a sudden, a blue flame－kinda like a spirit－enveloped the man!"

msgctxt "1052_Noa"
msgid "The yakuza saw it and ran away!"
msgstr "The yakuza saw it and ran away!"

msgctxt "1064_Noa"
msgid "It had to be the ghost!"
msgstr "It had to be the ghost!"

msgctxt "1076_Akiyama"
msgid "Wow... I had no idea."
msgstr "Wow... I had no idea."

msgctxt "1088_Akiyama"
msgid "Did you try out the footbaths at Yunosono?"
msgstr "¿Probaste los baños de pies en Yunosono?"

msgctxt "1100_Noa"
msgid "I did! The hot water was so refreshing! I felt brand new afterwards, like I was brought back to life."
msgstr "I did! The hot water was so refreshing! I felt brand new afterwards, like I was brought back to life."

msgctxt "1112_Akiyama"
msgid "Sounds like something an old man would say."
msgstr "Sounds like something an old man would say."

msgctxt "1124_Noa"
msgid "Oh yeah, I bet you'd know all about what old men say."
msgstr "Oh yeah, I bet you'd know all about what old men say."

msgctxt "1136_Akiyama"
msgid "Ouch."
msgstr "Ouch."

msgctxt "1148_Akiyama"
msgid "So, about those golf dates..."
msgstr "So, about those golf dates..."

msgctxt "1160_Noa"
msgid "The golf course is pretty far away, though. I tried driving there one time, it was so far I had to turn around halfway! At least I got a nice road trip out of it. ♪"
msgstr "The golf course is pretty far away, though. I tried driving there one time, it was so far I had to turn around halfway! At least I got a nice road trip out of it. ♪"

msgctxt "1172_Akiyama"
msgid "Guess that would make a pretty good date, too..."
msgstr "Guess that would make a pretty good date, too..."

msgctxt "1184_Akiyama"
msgid "Had any liver lately?"
msgstr "Had any liver lately?"

msgctxt "1196_Noa"
msgid "Yep. I ate yakiniku with a friend the other day."
msgstr "Síp. Comí yakiniku con un amiga el otro día."

msgctxt "1208_Akiyama"
msgid "Oh yeah? Try not to eat too much."
msgstr "Oh yeah? Try not to eat too much."

msgctxt "1220_Akiyama"
msgid "About that pole dancing workout..."
msgstr "Sobre hacer ejercicio con pole dance..."

msgctxt "1232_Noa"
msgid "You mentioned this before, didn't you? Hmm... Do you want to see me pole dance?"
msgstr "You mentioned this before, didn't you? Hmm... Do you want to see me pole dance?"

msgctxt "1244_Akiyama"
msgid "What? You'll show me?"
msgstr "What? You'll show me?"

msgctxt "1256_Noa"
msgid "Haha! No need to get so excited. I just wanted to see your reaction. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Haha! No need to get so excited. I just wanted to see your reaction. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "1268_Akiyama"
msgid "Did you try that sake we talked about? You know, the sweet kind?"
msgstr "¿Probaste el sake que te mencione? ¿El que era dulce?"

msgctxt "1280_Noa"
msgid "I did. It's really good, just like you said. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "I did. It's really good, just like you said. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "1292_Akiyama"
msgid "Isn't it? It proves that sake is great in all its forms."
msgstr "Isn't it? It proves that sake is great in all its forms."

msgctxt "1304_Noa"
msgid "Sweet sake doesn't fit your image, though."
msgstr "Sweet sake doesn't fit your image, though."

msgctxt "1316_Noa"
msgid "You look like a purist who would say, \"Sake must be dry! Sweet sake is heresy!\""
msgstr "You look like a purist who would say, \"Sake must be dry! Sweet sake is heresy!\""

msgctxt "1328_Akiyama"
msgid "Um... Okay..."
msgstr "Um... Okay..."

